{
  "stem": "1550.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I joined my parents on the on the-- which was the biggest ship with about 1,000 tons with 1,800 people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, the-- the overcrowding is difficult to describe, let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Try.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Try?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one time while traveling, it was so crowded that the ship started to lean over to one side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It leaned over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was-- it was-- how shall I put it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was too much weight near the top.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It leaned over to one side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, we had a-- we had a police on board of the ship of our own, like an order group.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were stationed at strategic points to-- to see that the traffic goes and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was also a member of that group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what-- what-- when that-- that happened quite frequently that the ship started to lean over to this side or to this side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So at that time, the order was everybody to the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- the language on board the ship was German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All these Jews were from Central Europe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It means everybody to the left or everybody to the right, whatever necessary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then the ship slowly righted itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Also, it was so crowded that two people couldn't pass each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So as a result, it was organized that if you want to go in this direction on deck, on a certain deck, you could go only in this direction.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the-- and to go back the other direction, you had to go on the other side of the ship.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was, you might say what was one-way traffic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The toilet facilities?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] The toilet facilities, there was some toilets there, but only for women with small children.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
